description: For sale: $174,900. MAJOR HOUSE CRUSH! This home nails the warm & cozy aesthetic...glossy subway tile, rich hardwood floors, & farmhouse lighting. Premium corner lot with darling curb appeal. A charming 4-season porch, 2 spacious main level bedrooms, & a huge upper level bedroom with adjoining nursery/playroom! The comfy den could easily become a 4th bedroom. The new lower-level bathroom features a sleek-meets-salvaged look that's polished & rustic all at once. Spectacular, resort-style fenced-in backyard with chic garden shed. Step up your entertaining game with the fire pit area & 2 patios! Newer major mechanicals! Keep your car tucked away in the attached garage. This home personifies the Farmhouse Industrial style, where rustic meets modern. It's family-friendly & comfortable...it's woods, whites, & metals. This is your happy place!

For sale: $37,500. Single wide 2000 Dutch mobile home. New roof 2016, New central air and furnace 2018, New carpeting installed 2018, New patio 2018, and comes with the shed and firepit. Beautifully kept, well decorated, affordable country living. Costs less than an apartment, and you can have pets. Lot rent includes water, septic, and garbage.

Backyard features include a patio, utility shed and a private fenced environment for backyard activities. The attached garage is insulated and heated. You don't want to miss out on this one!

For sale: $529,000. Prime location! Check out this custom rambler on 4 acres one mile south of Medford on tar road! This open floor plan home has 5 bedrooms, 3 1/2 baths and heated triple car garage. Amenities include fire place on upper and lower levels, hickory hardwood floors, solid cherry doors, stainless steel appliances, Cambria countertops, double master shower, in floor heat and irrigation system. Outdoor areas include a stamped patio, deck, fire pit and outbuilding.

For sale: $65,800. Move in ready. 28 ft x 70 ft mobile home. New roof and skylights. Open concept floor plan. Includes family room, living room, kitchen, dining room. Laundry room off kitchen, washer, dryer, chest freezer, lots of shelving. Kitchen has a full walk-in pantry. Stove, microwave, dishwasher, refrigerator, large island. Two bedrooms, master with two vanities, jet tub, separate shower and large walk-in closet, Rubbermaid shelving. Second bedroom, walk-in closet. Second full bathroom with tub and shower. Office/den, patio door walkout to a 28 x 14 covered deck. Home features natural gas heat, central air, freshly painted interior. Outside has a 10 x 12 shed, great workshop and storage area. Medford school district located at the Lazy U community.Lot rent is $360.00, includes soft-water, sewer and garbage.
